20:19.318 --> 20:21.548
[screaming]

20:24.289 --> 20:28.350
You know, if l'm not mistaken,
l think Daddy's scared his little boys.

20:34.366 --> 20:36.857
We got you good.

20:36.935 --> 20:39.199
Happy Halloween.

20:39.271 --> 20:41.239
Thanks a lot, Larry.
Come on up here.

20:41.306 --> 20:44.241
Listen, l gotta congratulate you people.

20:44.309 --> 20:48.473
l mean, in all my years l have never
seen a family go to such sick lengths

20:48.580 --> 20:50.480
