- l didn't do this. Larry, did you?

21:08.033 --> 21:09.864
Wish l had. lt's a nice touch.

21:09.935 --> 21:11.402
lt's shut. We're locked in.

21:11.470 --> 21:14.701
No worries. l'm the Tool Man.
l'll get it open.

21:14.773 --> 21:16.240
[pounding]

21:17.209 --> 21:19.541
