leave them up there?

21:19.611 --> 21:21.101
Long enough to let them know

21:21.179 --> 21:24.114
that Al Borland can prank
with the best of them.

21:24.182 --> 21:25.342
[chuckling]

21:25.450 --> 21:26.610
Actually, you know,

21:26.718 --> 21:30.154
maybe l should let them down now
before Tim does something stupid.

21:30.222 --> 21:32.190
[pounding]

21:48.840 --> 21:51.900
- [woman] There we go.
- Don't wipe him off.

21:51.977 --> 21:54.104
Don't wipe him off.

